{"data": [{"id": "4742132", "title": "Thoughtful Investments Are The Only Ones Worth Making", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Conceptual image of man using smartphone to view bar graph\" data-id=\"1359134494\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1138px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">We Are</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The Canadian government\u2019s plan to constrain population growth by reducing immigration over the next few years is designed to relieve demand pressure on key services like housing, education and health care. That\u2019s needed.</p> <p>The downsides are that</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742132-thoughtful-investments-only-ones-worth-making", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 22:10:00"}, {"id": "4742115", "title": "Ideaya Biosciences: Long-Tailed Pipeline With Positive Mid-Stage Data And Huge Cash", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business on Wall Street in Manhattan\" data-id=\"1220627489\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6240px\" height=\"4160px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Pgiam/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4656120-ideaya-biosciences-stock-an-opportunity-missed-rating-downgrade\">covered</a> <b>Ideaya Biosciences, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IDYA\" title=\"IDEAYA Biosciences, Inc.\">IDYA</a></span>) in December last year, and the stock had a great run for a while, before returning more or less to its December position. That \"idiopathic\" bullish run started in early January and continued</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742115-ideaya-biosciences-long-tailed-pipeline-with-positive-midstage-data-and-huge-cash", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 22:00:56"}, {"id": "4742126", "title": "Super Micro's Turning Point", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384239426/image_1384239426.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"3d rendering of crypto mining computer center\" data-id=\"1384239426\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384239426/image_1384239426.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384239426/image_1384239426.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384239426/image_1384239426.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384239426/image_1384239426.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384239426/image_1384239426.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384239426/image_1384239426.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384239426/image_1384239426.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384239426/image_1384239426.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">alvarez</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>Recent events at Super Micro Computer, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SMCI\" title=\"Super Micro Computer, Inc.\">SMCI</a></span>) have met our <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4732872-inside-super-micros-crisis-5-scenarios-that-could-define-its-future-rating-downgrade\">prior assumptions</a> very well. We anticipated stabilization after the appointment of a reputable auditor, and, sure enough, the Special Committee investigation is complete with </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384239426/image_1384239426.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742126-super-micro-turning-point", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 21:53:33"}, {"id": "4742109", "title": "Blue Bird Is Positioned For Continued Growth, Looks Even More Attractive Now", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1590616588/image_1590616588.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Yellow electric school bus plugged in at a charging station.\" data-id=\"1590616588\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1590616588/image_1590616588.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1590616588/image_1590616588.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1590616588/image_1590616588.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1590616588/image_1590616588.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1590616588/image_1590616588.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1590616588/image_1590616588.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1590616588/image_1590616588.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1590616588/image_1590616588.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">TW Farlow</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><span>The Thesis</span></h2> <p>Exiting FY24, the American bus manufacturing company Blue Bird Corporation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BLBD\" title=\"Blue Bird Corporation\">BLBD</a></span>) reported another quarter with double-digit top-line growth as the demand environment remained strong. While the overall demand looks robust, the anticipated decline in EV manufacturing</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1590616588/image_1590616588.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742109-blue-bird-positioned-for-continued-growth-even-more-attractive-now", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 21:46:27"}, {"id": "4742108", "title": "NVR, Inc.: Potentially Topping Out", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172406166/image_2172406166.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A man is explaining the project to three workers / students\" data-id=\"2172406166\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.