dn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200400114/image_200400114.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='Fruit machine bars spinning to line of 7\"s, close-up (blurred motion)' data-id=\"200400114-001\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1008px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200400114/image_200400114.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200400114/image_200400114.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200400114/image_200400114.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200400114/image_200400114.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200400114/image_200400114.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200400114/image_200400114.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200400114/image_200400114.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200400114/image_200400114.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Harrison Eastwood/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>Pure Storage, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PSTG\" title=\"Pure Storage, Inc.\">PSTG</a></span>) reported its <a href=\"https://investor.purestorage.com/financial-information/quarterly-results/default.aspx\" rel=\"nofollow\">3QFY25</a> earnings results after the bell on Tuesday, confirming its unique position within data storage with design wins from DirectFlash Technology with a \u201ctop-four hyperscaler.\u201d Charles Giancarlo, Pure Storage</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200400114/image_200400114.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742103-pure-storage-design-wins-keep-us-bullish", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 21:31:41"}, {"id": "4742117", "title": "Dividends By The Numbers In November 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1462296278/image_1462296278.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Bar graph of floating cash - Wave pattern\" data-id=\"1462296278\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1462296278/image_1462296278.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1462296278/image_1462296278.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1462296278/image_1462296278.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1462296278/image_1462296278.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1462296278/image_1462296278.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1462296278/image_1462296278.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1462296278/image_1462296278.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1462296278/image_1462296278.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The numbers for U.S. stock market dividends were bearish in November 2024.</p> <p>Standard &amp; Poor's dividend metadata for the month tells the tale. There were 43 fewer favorable changes recorded for November 2024 than were recorded in the same month</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1462296278/image_1462296278.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742117-dividends-by-the-numbers-in-november-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 21:25:00"}, {"id": "4742100", "title": "Sempra: Above-Average Growth Prospects For A Utility Company", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159343342/image_2159343342.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Digitally Generated Image of LNG Tanker Navigating Coastal Waters Representing Maritime Energy Transport\" data-id=\"2159343342\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"845px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159343342/image_2159343342.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159343342/image_2159343342.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159343342/image_2159343342.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159343342/image_2159343342.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159343342/image_2159343342.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159343342/image_2159343342.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159343342/image_2159343342.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159343342/image_2159343342.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">alvarez</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Today, I will take a look at San Diego, CA-based Sempra (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SRE\" title=\"Sempra\">SRE</a></span>). Sempra is considered a \"multi-utility\" company because it has significant operations in electric power generation, natural gas distribution, and the domestic and international liquid natural gas (\"LNG\") markets. In the United States, Sempra is</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159343342/image_2159343342.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742100-sempra-energy-above-average-growth-prospects-for-a-utility-company", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 21:12:39"}, {"id": "4742111", "title": "Why The Latest Corporate Earnings May Fuel Market Optimism In 2025", "description": "<p></p> <p><strong>Greg Bonnell:</strong> US markets have continued to climb to record highs this year, the S&amp;P 500 and the NASDAQ Composite both gaining another 5% in November alone. Well, my next guest says this is no longer a mega tech rally. So what is happening in the equity markets right now? Damian Fernandes, Managing Director and Portfolio Manager with TD Asset Management, joins us. Great to have you back on the program, Damian.</p> <p><strong>Damian Fernandes:</strong> Thanks, Greg. Always a pleasure to be on.</p> <p><strong>Greg Bonnell:</strong> All right. So here we are. We're in the last trading month of the year. Stocks have been on a record run. We just got through an earnings season. It's time to pick your brain as to what's going on.</p> <p><strong>Damian Fernandes:</strong> You know what? It's so much more enjoyable coming here on a bull market. It's the Christmas season. It's the gift of giving. And who doesn't love a big rip-roaring bull market to end the year?</p> <p><strong>Greg Bonnell:</strong> So let's talk about what got us here, what is going on, and, well, maybe we can dig into earnings, too. I mean, we're past the bulk of it in the States.</p> <p><strong>Damian Fernandes:</strong> Sure, yeah.</p> <p><strong>Greg Bonnell:</strong> Did it show you something to justify what we're seeing in the markets?</p> <p><strong>Damian Fernandes:</strong> Yeah, so if I split that into two things-- what got us here. What got us here is actually a pretty favorable backdrop. I know that might seem -- might seem difficult just because it seems so volatile politically, geopolitically, macro. But when you look at the fundamentals that drive stocks, earnings for 2024 are going to be up about 10%. We just had-- we had a pretty good earnings quarter.</p> <p>Last year, inflation was still running hot. Central banks had started easing. But as we've</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742111-why-the-latest-corporate-earnings-may-fuel-market-optimism-in-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 21:10:00"}, {"id": "4742098", "title": "ETB: Providing A Distribution Rate Of ~8.5% With Monthly Pay", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810174/image_1445810174.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Saving time\" data-id=\"1445810174\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1055px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810174/image_1445810174.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810174/image_1445810174.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810174/image_1445810174.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810174/image_1445810174.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810174/image_1445810174.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 